</p><p class="- topic/p ">The internal software estimator is at the hardstop level and the ink level high sensor is active. The ink level estimator in software is deviating too much. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><tsBody class="- topic/body tsTroubleshooting/tsBody "><tsSymptoms id="GUID-33E1B64A-E818-4500-A780-C8BC692D14B2" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsSymptoms "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></tsSymptoms><tsCauses id="GUID-645FA0EC-F3F0-411D-8024-E1FB1B9CEBFB" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsCauses "><p class="- topic/p ">Pumps are not pumping ink. The ink level estimator is deviating too much. 
</p></tsCauses><tsDiagnose id="GUID-65699D71-F589-4C0A-824B-610B2BC799FC" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsDiagnose "><p class="- topic/p ">In case the tube is not in the pump, the ink estimator is deviating too much. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Typically this happens after initial filling of the printheads. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove so much ink from the jar, that the ink level is lower than the high sensor. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The system will request for new ink, and add a new bottle of ink via the normal operator procedure. 
</p><note id="GUID-5C37023F-7787-44A6-AD9E-68EA51FCC08C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Due to adding the 2<sup class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sup ">nd</sup> bottle of ink, the ink loading procedure can not be shown to the customer immediately after the installation. 
</p></note><note id="GUID-5D0D1EC2-D815-4C16-AB2D-7421D35E9A2E" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">When ink loading is not possible, this can be due to the normal timeout of 15 minutes required for draining after loading the bottle. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A restart of the engine (MRE) will re-trigger the 15 minute timeout. 
</p></note></tsDiagnose><tsCauses id="GUID-CFE6A853-BA2D-456F-AC0E-3C927B16AA66" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsCauses "><p class="- topic/p ">Blocking mechanism in the ink loading interface is malfunctioning. 
</p></tsCauses><tsDiagnose id="GUID-96A5BE54-366A-4D18-A85F-A90AAC900433" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsDiagnose "><p class="- topic/p ">In case ink levers are not blocked after loading the bottle and the levers are moved, the estimators will be off. 
</p></tsDiagnose><tsCauses id="GUID-1F967755-65F4-41AF-A94B-3E033CB02923" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsCauses "><p class="- topic/p ">Ink level in the ink tank 
</p></tsCauses><tsDiagnose id="GUID-2480E015-1AE2-4D8B-86CE-6589A4BA2744" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsDiagnose "><p class="- topic/p ">Check / Refill the ink level in the ink tank (C, Y, M, K or W). 
